author: COMSOL
description: A capacitive micromachined ultrasonic transducer (CMUT) converts ultrasound to an electrical signal for high-resolution imaging applications. This tutorial demonstrates how a lumped model of a MEMS transducer can be derived from its FEM model. It includes an FEM model of a CMUT and the corresponding lumped model created using the Lumped Mechanical System (LMS) interface. The parameters of the LMS model are obtained from the Parameter Estimation study.
